# epam-cli — Project Rules

For full project standards, architecture notes, and guardrails see **CLAUDE.md** in the repository root.

## Critical: Node.js Version
Do NOT use the system `node` binary (v14). Always invoke via:
`~/.nvm/versions/node/v20.20.0/bin/node`

## Quick Reference
- **Build**: `~/.nvm/versions/node/v20.20.0/bin/node ./node_modules/.bin/tsup`
- **Test**: `~/.nvm/versions/node/v20.20.0/bin/node ./node_modules/.bin/vitest run`
- **Type check**: `npx tsc --noEmit`

## Guardrails (summary — see CLAUDE.md for full list)
- Never force-push to main/master
- Never commit secrets, .env files, or API keys
- Run all 42 tests before any PR
- Never log PII to any monitoring system
